author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-‍Midelfart Capital solds its 3 mln Storebrand shares
text:
Feb 21 (Reuters) - Storebrand Asa:
* ‍MIDELFART CAPITAL AS HAS, ON 20 FEB 2017, SOLD 3,000,000 SHARES IN STOREBRAND AT NOK 68,15​
* ‍AFTER THIS TRANSACTION MIDELFART WILL NOT HAVE ANY SHARES IN STOREBRAND​
* ‍MIDELFART HAS, SINCE SEPTEMBER 2015, BEEN REPRESENTED ON BOARD OF DIRECTORS OF STOREBRAND BY MR. HÅKON R. FURE​ Further company coverage: (Reporting By Terje Solsvik)
